
==  Structures_DataGrid Unit Tests ==

To run the tests you need:
- PHP5
- PHPUnit >= 3.1.0RC1 from http://phpunit.de/

You can run one test suite at a time ; example:

$ phpunit DataSourceMDB2Test.php

Remark: simply running "phpunit" may fail on your system, if that's the case
try "php5 /usr/bin/phpunit" or "php /usr/bin/phpunit"

You can also run a group of test suites:

$ phpunit AllDataSourceTests.php

Or all:

$ phpunit AllTests.php

If something seems wrong, look at the verbose output with:

$ phpunit --verbose AllTests.php

If you have your Structures_DataGrid files in a special location, set the
include_path with something like:

$ php5 -d 'include_path=.:/special/location:/path/to/pear' /usr/bin/phpunit AllTests.php

where /path/to/pear may be /usr/share/php if you're on a unix-like system.



